1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:12,400
On fariseos* okimatkej ika Jesús kimpiyaya más inomachtijkauan* niman más tlakuatekiyaya xken Juan.

2
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:15,120
Pero Jesús xyejua tlakuatekiyaya,

3
00:00:15,120 --> 00:00:18,400
yej san inomachtijkauan* tlakuatekiyayaj.

4
00:00:18,400 --> 00:00:21,100
Niman ijkuak Jesús ijkon okimat,

5
00:00:21,100 --> 00:00:25,640
okis ne Judea para oksejpa oyaj Galilea.

6
00:00:25,640 --> 00:00:27,800
Niman ipan iojui,

7
00:00:27,800 --> 00:00:32,160
ika onkatka para panos ipan iueyitlalpan Samaria.

8
00:00:32,160 --> 00:00:33,400
Oajsik tej,

9
00:00:33,400 --> 00:00:36,720
ipan on kalpan Sicar de Samaria.

10
00:00:36,720 --> 00:00:43,840
Yejua in kalpan onkatka san nisiu itech on tlajli yejuan Jacob okimakak José on ikoneu.

11
00:00:43,840 --> 00:00:50,320
Ompa onkatka sen atlaltekontli*  yejuan kuitiayaj iatlaltekon Jacob.

12
00:00:50,320 --> 00:00:56,080
Jesús onotlalij itenko on atlaltekontli* pampa uajsiautiaya ipan iojui.

13
00:00:56,080 --> 00:00:58,960
Ijkuakon katka kanaj tlakualispan.

14
00:00:58,960 --> 00:01:04,360
Inomachtijkauan oyajkej ipan on kalpan para okouatoj itlaj tlen kikuaskej.

15
00:01:04,360 --> 00:01:08,480
Kemaj ouajlaj sen siuatl yejuan chanej* ne Samaria.

16
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:13,040
Yejua ouajlaj para okixtiko atl ijtik on atlaltekontli*,

17
00:01:13,040 --> 00:01:14,680
niman Jesús okijlij:

18
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:16,800
—Xnechmaka atl.

19
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:20,600
Kemaj on siuatl samaritana okijlij Jesús:

20
00:01:20,600 --> 00:01:27,480
—¿Kenijki tejua yejuan tihebreo* tinechtlajtlanilia atl nejua yejuan nisamaritana?

21
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:32,840
Ijkin okijtoj pampa on hebreos* xkuajli nouikayaj inuan on samaritanos.

22
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:34,760
Kemaj Jesús okijlij:

23
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:39,720
—Tla tikmatiskia ika Dios kineki mitsmakas sen kuajli tetlayokolijli*,

24
00:01:39,720 --> 00:01:43,040
niman akin nejua yejuan nimitstlajtlanilijtikaj atl,

25
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:43,720
tla ijkon,

26
00:01:43,720 --> 00:01:49,520
yej tejua tinechtlajtlaniliskia atl niman nejua nimitsmakaskia on atl yejuan kitemaka nemilistli.

27
00:01:49,520 --> 00:01:51,520
On siuatl okijlij:

28
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:53,160
—Señor,

29
00:01:53,160 --> 00:02:00,600
nion siquiera xtikpiya tlinon ika tikixtis on atl niman in atlaltekontli* sanoyej* uejkatlan.

30
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:06,780
¿Kanon tikonkuis on atl yejuan kitemaka nemilistli para tinechmakas?

31
00:02:06,780 --> 00:02:16,000
¿Tlen tejua tiknemilia más tiueyixtikaj xken on toachtojtataj Jacob yejuan otechmakak in atlaltekontli*?

32
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:19,120
Yejua nikan atliya niman no ikoneuan,

33
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:22,600
niman iyolkauan atliyaj nikan.

34
00:02:22,600 --> 00:02:23,960
Jesús okijlij:

35
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:27,120
—On akin koni in atl oksejpa amiki.

36
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:31,680
Pero akin konis on atl yejuan nikmakas xkaman amikis,

37
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:39,200
pampa on atl yejuan nikmakas yejua ijtik ken itlaj ameyajli yejuan kimakas nemilistli para nochipa.

38
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:41,160
Kemaj on siuatl okijlij:

39
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:42,440
—Señor,

40
00:02:42,440 --> 00:02:46,120
xnechmaka on atl para maka oksejpa namikis,

41
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:51,060
nion niuajlas nikuajkixtis atl ijtik in atlaltekontli*.

42
00:02:51,060 --> 00:02:52,360
Jesús okijlij:

43
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:57,440
—Xuiya xkanati moueuentsin niman kemaj xuajlakan nikan.

44
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:59,960
Niman on siuatl ijkin okinankilij:

45
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:02,400
—Xnikpiya noueuentsin.

46
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:04,540
Kemaj Jesús okijlij:

47
00:03:04,540 --> 00:03:07,560
—On ika otikijtoj xtikpiya moueuentsin,

48
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,640
on melauak,

49
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:11,760
pampa makuijli moueuentsitsiuan yotikimpix,

50
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:15,280
niman on yejuan aman tikpiya xmoueuentsin.

51
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:18,180
Yejua ika on melauak tlen otikijtoj.

52
00:03:18,180 --> 00:03:21,120
Niman ijkuak on siuatl ijkon okak,

53
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,560
okijlij Jesús:

54
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:24,000
—Señor,

55
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:27,920
nejua nikita ika tejua titiotlajtojketl.

56
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:33,640
On toachtojtajuan samaritanos okimauistilijkej Dios nikan ipan in tepetl,

57
00:03:33,640 --> 00:03:41,200
pero nemejuamej yejuan nenhebreos* nenkijtouaj ika noneki tikmauistiliskej ne Jerusalén.

58
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:42,920
Jesús okijlij:

59
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:44,160
—Siuatl,

60
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:48,960
xnechneltokili ika uajlau on tonaltin ijkuak nion nikan ipan in tepetl,

61
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:52,520
nion ne Jerusalén xnenkimauistiliskej Dios.

62
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:57,800
Nemejuamej yejuan nensamaritanos xnenkimatij akinon nenkimauistiliaj,

63
00:03:57,800 --> 00:04:05,020
pero tejuamej yejuan tihebreos* tikmatij akinon tikmauistiliaj pampa on temakixtilistli kisa totech.

64
00:04:05,020 --> 00:04:11,840
Pero uajlau on tonajli niman sano aman ijkuak on yejuan melauak kinekij kimauistiliaj toTajtsin,

65
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:17,420
kimauistiliskej impan inyojlo niman ika tlen melauak ken Dios kineki.

66
00:04:17,420 --> 00:04:19,080
ToTajtsin tej,

67
00:04:19,080 --> 00:04:22,720
ijki kineki ma kichiuakan on yejuan kimauistiliaj.

68
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:24,520
Dios yejua Espíritu,

69
00:04:24,520 --> 00:04:32,020
niman on yejuan kimauistiliaj ika onkaj kichiuaskej ikan iminespíritu niman ika tlen melauak ken Dios kineki.

70
00:04:32,020 --> 00:04:33,560
On siuatl okijlij:

71
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:37,120
—Nejua nikmatstikaj ika uajlas on Mesías,

72
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:39,760
on yejuan itoka Cristo.

73
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:41,760
Ijkuak yejua uajlas,

74
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:44,980
nochi tlajtlamach* techmelajkaijlis.

75
00:04:44,980 --> 00:04:47,080
Niman Jesús okijlij:

76
00:04:47,080 --> 00:04:50,740
—Sano nejua yejuan nimitsnojnotstikaj.

77
00:04:50,740 --> 00:04:59,540
Niman kemaj oyejkokej on inomachtijkauan* niman okintlatlachaltij ika Jesús tlajtlajtouaya iuan sen siuatl.

78
00:04:59,540 --> 00:05:03,260
Pero xakaj okitlajtoltij tlinon kinekiya on siuatl,

79
00:05:03,260 --> 00:05:07,020
noso tline* tlajtlajtouaya Jesús iuan on siuatl.

80
00:05:07,020 --> 00:05:13,540
Kemaj on siuatl okajteu itsotsokol niman oyaj okiteijlito ipan on ueyikalpan:

81
00:05:13,540 --> 00:05:14,920
—Xuajlakan,

82
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:19,960
xkitakij sen tlakatl yejuan onechpanextijlij nochi tlen yonikchiu.

83
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:22,000
¿Manin xyejua Cristo?

84
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,200
Kemaj,

85
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:29,120
on tlakamej okiskej ipan on ueyikalpan niman oyajkej ne kampa nemiya Jesús.

86
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:31,240
Chika in nochijtikatka,

87
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:33,960
on inomachtijkauan* Jesús kijliayaj:

88
00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:35,560
—Temachtijketl,

89
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:37,360
nimantsin xtlakua.

90
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,980
Pero yejua okinmijlij:

91
00:05:38,980 --> 00:05:43,540
—Nejua nikpiya tlen nikuas yejuan nemejuamej xnenkimatij.

92
00:05:43,540 --> 00:05:46,320
Ijkuak on nomachtijkej* ijkon okakkej,

93
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:48,140
opeu notlajtoltiaj:

94
00:05:48,140 --> 00:05:50,920
—¿Manin yej yakaj yokitlakualtiko?

95
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:53,140
Pero Jesús okinmijlij:

96
00:05:53,140 --> 00:05:57,240
—Ijkon ken nemotlalnakayo kojtitikaj ijkuak nentlakuaj,

97
00:05:57,240 --> 00:06:04,960
no ijki noalma kojtitikaj ijkuak nikchiua tlen kineki on yejuan onechajtitlan para nitlamis itekiu.

98
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:06,180
Yejua ika tej,

99
00:06:06,180 --> 00:06:08,500
in tekitl sano ijki ken notlakual.

100
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:10,580
Nemejuamej nenkijtouaj:

101
00:06:10,580 --> 00:06:13,620
“Sanken* poliui naui metstli para pixkalos.”

102
00:06:13,620 --> 00:06:15,600
Pero nejua nemechijlia:

103
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:18,360
Xkintakan nochimej on tlaltikpaktlakamej.

104
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:23,680
Yejuamej no ijki ken se ueyi tlatoktli yejuan yochikau para nopixkas.

105
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:27,920
On yejuan kimpixka inalmas on tlakamej kiselia itlaxtlauil,

106
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:31,920
niman on yejuan kimpixkaj kiseliskej nemilistli para nochipa.

107
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:32,740
Tla ijkon tej,

108
00:06:32,740 --> 00:06:37,080
on yejuan tlatôka niman on yejuan pixka san sekan pakiskej.

109
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:37,880
Tla ijkon,

110
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:39,900
melauak ken kijtoua sen tlajtojli:

111
00:06:39,900 --> 00:06:42,920
“Se tlatôka niman okse pixka.”

112
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:47,680
Nejua onemechtitlan xpixkatij ne kampa xonentokakej.

113
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:53,440
Oksekimej otekitkej niman nemejuamej sa nenkiseliaj on tlen yokitekitkej.

114
00:06:53,440 --> 00:07:04,060
Niman miyekej samaritanos yejuan chanejkej ipan on ueyikalpan okineltokakej Jesús ipampa on tlen okinmijlij on siuatl ijkuak okinmijli:

115
00:07:04,060 --> 00:07:07,780
“Onechpanextilij nochi tlen nejua yonikchiu.”

116
00:07:07,780 --> 00:07:09,160
Yejua ika,

117
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:12,240
ijkuak on chanejkej Samaria oualajkej,

118
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:19,580
sanoyej okitlajtlanilijkej para ompa inuan ma nokaua niman Jesús ome tonajli ompa onokau.

119
00:07:19,580 --> 00:07:26,140
Niman miyekej más otlaneltokakej ijkuak okakkej on tlen sano yejua kijtouaya.

120
00:07:26,140 --> 00:07:28,840
Kemaj okijlijkej on siuatl:

121
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:33,220
—Aman tikneltokaj xsan pampa on tlen otitechijlij,

122
00:07:33,220 --> 00:07:37,280
yej no pampa sano tejuamej yotikakkej.

123
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:46,440
Niman tikmatstokej ika melauak yejua temakixtijketl yejuan kinmakixtis on tlaltikpaktlakamej.

